statement.p:
Compute the logarithms.



\log_3 9 = 2 because 3^2=9


\log_5 125 = 3 because 5^3=125


\log_4 \dfrac{1}{16} = -2 because 4^{-2}=\dfrac{1}{16}


\log_5 \sqrt{5} = \dfrac{1}{2} because 5^{1/2} = \sqrt{5}

